{"tid":2066951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星火係咪經常唔理人？","createTime":"2020-06-16T15:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T01:13:15.000Z","uid":262172,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f00c7406d44181fb12a6a152f436125d9850beee","tid":2066951,"uid":262172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:47:18.000Z","msg":"手足被捕出事去搵佢地，已經成個禮拜冇覆，612亦唔批錢，為運動犧牲左好既手足開始心灰意冷，問究竟係唔係香港人已經忘記左佢地，丟低佢地。我遇到幾個手足，都係話星火唔理人唔覆人，想問問有幾多被捕手足有遇過呢d問題？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hV17R7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hV17R7.jpg&h=317b730c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzCTexv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzCTexv.jpg&h=176fbd74&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vxms3re.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxms3re.jpg&h=7e27beb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MWNPxos.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWNPxos.png&h=4feeaee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fb5p5Jy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffb5p5Jy.png&h=36424ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張係佢同612對話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cqqp5E1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqqp5E1.jpg&h=1d71004c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人係唔係忘記左佢地我唔知，但我好想知星火同612係唔係已經冇做野？手足犧牲左咁多，個個精神都好差，連個後援都冇，好難唔令人覺得香港人已經遺棄左佢地！我想問依家係唔係捐星火都係幫唔到手足？"},{"pid":"c8b88a239c9840138c94d12f86bbc28853851001","tid":2066951,"uid":68186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:50:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33b78d47491a32556e86a01690a02d769ad36f73","tid":2066951,"uid":64582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:56:35.000Z","msg":"星火仲有錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c584ea7620eeb6e4a8c83d56db0c1aedca7688","tid":2066951,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"咁多人要幫 邊幫得晒咁多人"},{"pid":"ac6c46e7f3ad137629786f2684ff1ffbedc49116","tid":2066951,"uid":15954,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:04:44.000Z","msg":"星火唔係比港共抄左家咩"},{"pid":"83f6cd7b1cea4e9827732a1ce8921671095ca53b","tid":2066951,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"搵蕭生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能仲好dd"},{"pid":"bc4359505f374a1e372a162da9c3f34a657c8778","tid":2066951,"uid":358333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"五毛又搞分化"},{"pid":"575666cc2ae5ec9ae578d672843e37f3d709e8d6","tid":2066951,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"睇醫生要收據有咩問題...."},{"pid":"216d0c1c7f635dc1e8d0ffe2a1ffdb7926bfa7af","tid":2066951,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"星火好似收左皮?<br />\n一下冇左幾千萬"},{"pid":"6f2a9693f665fcb26ba4d55abe9616fbb6da1d95","tid":2066951,"uid":122270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"星火比人暫停左合共7千萬的帳戶 所有錢都拎唔到出黎 點做野啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9672db60fa83dfcc441d8c141044ab0e97548330","tid":2066951,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"星火個朵一路都差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前已經唔少人講過搵唔到星火<br />\n<br />\n最後都係claim 612"},{"pid":"dac91468e6c22ab1264338dee0bb95fa67480645","tid":2066951,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"唔係想質疑但想問清楚個情況<br />\n內文同第一張cap圖話事主係被捕嘅手足, 但同612嘅對話又話自己仲未被捕, 係同612對話時情況唔update定點? <br />\n如果同612係之前對話過, 被捕後冇再搵過612, 我覺得可以叫手足再試下搵多次612, 始終情況唔同, 結果可能都唔同<br />\n<br />\n<co